sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant C as Client
    participant O1 as Origin A
    participant R as Redis
    participant O2 as Origin B
    participant Recv as Receiver
    C->>O1: POST /events/abc + body
    O1->>R: EVALSHA append.lua — durable append
    O1-->>C: 204 · the byte is committed
    Note over O1: crash before OnStreamAppend fires the wake
    Note over R: cursor < tail · no wake armed · wake lost
    loop recovery sweep · every 2s on every origin
        O2->>R: SMEMBERS ds:{__ds}:subs · HasPendingWork per sub
        Note over O2: cursor < tail → a wake is owed
        O2->>R: EVALSHA arm_wake.lua — generation++ · re-fire
        O2->>Recv: POST webhook · delivered after Origin A is gone
        Recv-->>O2: 200 {done:true}
        O2->>R: EVALSHA ack.lua — cursor → tail
    end
